		<li><strong>Written agreement:</strong> Document any cost sharing or design agreements</li>
		<li><strong>Permit copies:</strong> Share permit information with neighbors</li>
		<li><strong>Photo documentation:</strong> Take before photos of property conditions</li>
		<li><strong>Contractor details:</strong> Provide neighbor with contractor contact info</li>
	</ul>

