		<li><strong>Dispute resolution:</strong> HOA may have its own mediation process</li>
		<li><strong>Three-way disputes:</strong> Conflicts between neighbors + HOA more complex</li>
		<li><strong>Review CC&Rs first:</strong> HOA rules may be more restrictive than city codes</li>
	</ul>

