	<p>Corner lots face unique fence challenges:</p>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Two front yards:</strong> Often have two sides subject to front yard height limits</li>
		<li><strong>Visibility triangle:</strong> Area near corner must remain low for traffic safety</li>
		<li><strong>Setback rules:</strong> More restrictive requirements on corner lots</li>
		<li><strong>Multiple neighbors:</strong> More adjoining properties = more potential disputes</li>
		<li><strong>Extra regulations:</strong> City may have special corner lot fence rules</li>
		<li><strong>Recommendation:</strong> Consult Planning Department before any corner lot fence</li>
	</ul>

